797
00:58:56,908 --> 00:58:57,951
Let's go.

798
00:58:59,160 --> 00:59:00,745
I have to go to work.

799
00:59:01,037 --> 00:59:03,498
Come on. I know you have some time left.

800
00:59:06,626 --> 00:59:09,754
-Deal.
-Deal. Come on, let's go.

801
00:59:10,088 --> 00:59:13,132
You did such a great job.

802
00:59:19,556 --> 00:59:20,598
Hello?

803
00:59:21,975 --> 00:59:22,976
Yes.

804
00:59:25,186 --> 00:59:26,229
Sorry?

805
00:59:27,939 --> 00:59:30,191
EMERGENCY MEDICAL CENTER

806
00:59:56,384 --> 00:59:58,052
I thought you might be scared.

807
00:59:58,136 --> 00:59:59,846
Hey, Jeong-hu.

808
01:00:03,891 --> 01:00:06,811
Jun-u. I'm sorry for everything.

809
01:00:07,687 --> 01:00:11,065
Jeong-hu. Our lives are not
that messed up after all.

810
01:00:12,108 --> 01:00:14,402
No. Who cares if we were born
a bit miserably?

811
01:00:14,485 --> 01:00:16,654
We can overcome it. Don't you think so?

812
01:00:34,589 --> 01:00:36,466
FUNERAL HALL, MORTUARY

813
01:00:36,549 --> 01:00:40,595
LATE SHIN JEONG-HU

814
01:00:51,981 --> 01:00:53,066
Jun-u.

815
01:00:55,610 --> 01:00:57,153
I brought your classmates.

816
01:00:58,905 --> 01:00:59,781
Are you okay?

817
01:01:04,160 --> 01:01:06,913
Why don't we wait outside? Let's go.

818
01:01:21,761 --> 01:01:23,054
I guess he has no family.

819
01:01:23,137 --> 01:01:25,973
He has a father,
but we can't reach him yet.

820
01:01:26,057 --> 01:01:27,809
His grandmother is at a nursing home

821
01:01:27,892 --> 01:01:29,143
due to Alzheimer's.

822
01:01:32,355 --> 01:01:34,607
Jun-u probably hasn't had anything to eat.

823
01:01:37,402 --> 01:01:40,571
Shall we go get something to eat?

824
01:01:40,655 --> 01:01:42,990
-Shall we?
-I'll go.

825
01:01:48,621 --> 01:01:49,997
Get it over with and come back out.

826
01:01:50,081 --> 01:01:53,209
I think they're the assailants.

827
01:01:56,212 --> 01:01:57,213
What is going on?

828
01:02:48,931 --> 01:02:50,016
Let's go.

829
01:02:58,065 --> 01:02:59,442
I guess that bastard didn't come.

830
01:03:01,027 --> 01:03:03,321
Do you know Lee Gi-tae? In your class.

831
01:03:05,323 --> 01:03:08,075
He paid us money to get you expelled.

832
01:03:12,580 --> 01:03:14,624
I was going to quit after just one time.

833
01:03:14,874 --> 01:03:16,876
Geon-hyeok, let's go.

834
01:03:38,815 --> 01:03:40,107
Because you were out of line.

835
01:03:41,734 --> 01:03:45,404
You started to raise doubts about me
instead of getting lost quietly.

836
01:03:45,655 --> 01:03:46,781
How dare you do that...

837
01:03:48,991 --> 01:03:50,076
to me.

838
01:04:35,288 --> 01:04:37,039
Jun-u, stop!

839
01:05:14,869 --> 01:05:16,704
Did you give them money? Are you crazy?

840
01:05:16,787 --> 01:05:18,289
Do you think he'll have your back?

841
01:05:18,372 --> 01:05:20,207
My friend died because of you guys.

842
01:05:20,291 --> 01:05:21,709
I'll get on my knees.

843
01:05:21,792 --> 01:05:23,878
Your life is already ruined,
but mine is different.

844
01:05:23,961 --> 01:05:26,297
Why didn't you hit him back
when Jun-u was hitting you?

845
01:05:26,380 --> 01:05:27,965
Were you upset that I beat up Hwi-yeong?

846
01:05:28,049 --> 01:05:29,884
I wanted to help
in case you were treated unfairly.

847
01:05:29,967 --> 01:05:31,052
Why would you help me?

848
01:05:31,135 --> 01:05:32,219
Out of pity?

849
01:05:32,845 --> 01:05:35,348
You can say exactly what you saw, right?

850
01:05:35,431 --> 01:05:36,474
Thank you, Geon-hyeok.

851
01:05:36,557 --> 01:05:38,142
Mom, help me.

852
01:05:38,225 --> 01:05:40,227
-Are you embarrassed?
-Did you give birth to me

853
01:05:40,311 --> 01:05:41,687
just to brag to others?

854
01:05:41,771 --> 01:05:43,064
I won't make it to SNU.

855
01:05:43,230 --> 01:05:45,358
-Are you okay?
-And why do I want to help you?

856
01:05:45,441 --> 01:05:46,943
Is it out of pity?

857
01:05:53,908 --> 01:05:56,118
Subtitle translation by Wayne Ryu

